airBaltic Club – a loyalty programme for every traveller!
Join airBaltic Club now and start collecting points and stamps!

Main features:

• Use digital card or add it to your Wallet to collect points;
• Check your airBaltic Club point balance and transactions;
• Join stamp card and collect stamps to receive valuable prizes;
• Get notified about latest offers and exclusive discounts;
• Receive instant prizes at Shake&Win raffle - just open the app, shake your mobile device and win;
• Book and check in for airBaltic flights, manage your booking and enhance your trip with additional services – baggage, seat reservation, meal on board and many others.

Earn points with partners, spend points on prizes!

• Collect points every time you fly with airBaltic or use the services of other partners - Booking.com, Rentalcars.com, LSG Sky Chefs and others;
• Use accrued points to treat yourself with gifts - reward flights to more than 70 destinations as well as flight upgrade to Business class, airBaltic gift cards, baggage vouchers and other compelling rewards.


Collect even more points, travel features and get a reward flight faster with the stamp card!


• Download the airBaltic Club mobile app and tap the Stamp card icon;
• Start collecting stamps to receive valuable prizes - flight discounts, reward flight, seat reservation and heavy cabin baggage voucher as well as bonus points;
• The more you fly, the more benefits you get! 

Don’t miss amazing rewards - join airBaltic Club, download the app and start now!

